source.name: Quick Stats
source.description: Quick Stats is the National Agricultural Statistics Service's online, self-service tool to access complete results from the 1997, 2002, and 2007 Censuses of Agriculture. The census collects data on all commodities produced on U.S. farms and ranches, as well as detailed information on expenses, income, and operator characteristics.
